title: Slow Love
description: A lonely snail lookin' for love literally crashes into the treehouse and asks Finn and Jake for help. Now, our heroes must teach this snail how to get a girlfriend before he destroys their home!

title: Frog Seasons, Autumn
description: Finn and Jake follow a frog carrying a crown across spring, summer, fall, and winter.

title: The Eyes
description: One night, an exhausted Finn and Jake are creeped out by an odd-looking horse that mysteriously appears outside the treehouse and keeps them awake. They try everything they can think of to get rid of the freaky horse, but nothing seems to work.

description: Finn teaches us about how the food chain works, through song.

title: Ghost Princess
description: Finn and Jake try to solve Ghost Princess' unsolved murder.

title: Through the Years: Princess Bubblegum
description: From a tiny gumball, to ruler of the Candy Kingdom, and now a great Warrior Princess! Not to mention those fun outfits! Check out the evolution of Princess Bubblegum throughout 10 years of Adventure Time!

title: I Remember You Music Video
description: Bringing you another Adventure Time slow jam, it's Marceline and Ice King.

title: Simon and Marcy's Origin Story
description: 996 years ago, a man named Simon Petrikov met a little girl named Marceline at the end of the Great Mushroom War, and they became great friends.

title: Through the Years: Jake the Dog
description: Jake the Dog to Jake the Blue Alien... Winged... Dog? Whatever you call him now, there's no denying Jake is the master of shape-shifting, sage advice, and bacon pancakes! Watch Jake's transformation throughout 10 seasons of Adventure Time!

title: Blood Under the Skin
description: Finn goes on an embarrassing quest to get armor to fit in with some really cool knights.

title: Marceline Song Music Video
description: A song about Marceline written by Casey James Basichis.

description: OH. MY. GLOB. These are the best Lumpy Space Princess freak out moments. Which one is your favorite?

description: Jake takes a vow of non-violence, which is inconvenient when they're attacked by marauders from the crystal dimension.

title: Another Way
description: The tears of a crying Cyclops just might heal Finn and Jake's broken toes.

title: Through the Years: Finn the Human
description: Adventurer. Hero. Puncher of buns. Finn has come a long way from Boom Boom Mountain! Watch Finn grow up throughout 10 years of Adventure Time!

title: Sow, Do You Like Them Apples
description: Ice King and Marceline are hungry for a snack.

title: Storytelling
description: When Jake becomes sick, the only thing that can cure him is a good story, so he asks Finn to go out and find one. The story must have excitement, romance, suspense and, of course, a happy ending. When nothing interesting happens, Finn tries to make the story happen, accidentally turning the forest animals against each other and him!

title: Power Animal
description: Finn is kidnapped by a group of gnomes, who want to harness his energy to take over the world. Only Jake can save his best friend if he can just focus long enough to follow the obvious clues and rescue Finn.

title: It Came From the Nightosphere
description: Against Marceline's wishes, Finn conjures her father, the Lord of Evil, and attempts to reconcile their rocky relationship. But when the Lord of Evil discovers his daughter has turned the family axe into a bass guitar, he takes it from her and starts sucking up all the souls in Ooo! Finn must find a way to stop the Lord of Evil and get Marceline's guitar back.

title: Craziest Characters
description: Lemongrab, Ricardio, the Clown Nurse. Which one is the all time craziest character on Adventure Time?

title: Paper Pete
description: The pages of the books in the Ooo library turn to Finn and Jake for help before the evil Moldari destroy them.

title: All's Well That Rats Swell
description: BMO wages war against a rat in the tree house, and Finn and Jake get sick.

title: Best Friends in the World Music Video
description: Finn sings to his friends. Written by Rebecca Sugar and Tim Kiefer.

title: Loyalty to the King
description: There's a new "Nice King" in Ooo, and he looks kinda like someone else we know.
